{
  "stem": "27409.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I was ordered demobilized from Strozhnitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There at the bank I had my own name, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I returned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] where [INAUDIBLE] which I had many [INAUDIBLE], and dark hair I had that I wasn't grey.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I learnt also a bit of Georgian, [INAUDIBLE] speaking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some called Singerian, some Singer, but they some [INAUDIBLE] one they were thinking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Didn't me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always did my job, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody liked to go in a reconnaissance over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was dropped in behind the enemy lines, you again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, it was a job which I could do, and [INAUDIBLE] I had [INAUDIBLE] give [INAUDIBLE] they were attacking headquarters for my group, specialist group.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they're attacking headquarter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They went and stormed, sometime they're killed, some of ours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And found the headquarter and stole-- brought papers back you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Lot of cyphers and numbers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it turned out it was a tank-- a tank unit, armored unit, which before the war was a cavalry unit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Germans, they're precision had the list of their hay and all the supplies which they had-- how many kilos for so many horses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were thinking it's a code, and brought it under danger back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my job, when it was going out, was leading them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and certain [INAUDIBLE] document was-- was of interest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had more-- very few which were specialists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was garroting the German guards and to enter there, and other opened every safe which was Percival.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He has sensitive finger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was from prison, liberated especially for the job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my second in command was a-- the secretary was a young communist of the unit, commissar, Alexander [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naza ?] Sasha [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Soloviov, ?] which was a very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
